d9561215960f50868a","tid":515823,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"從側拍影片來看，裴珍映站在黃旼炫、尹智聖中間，因防彈少年團成員V跟Jimin要從他們面前走過、繞去座後面的位子，當他發現Jimin走了過來後，眼神就一直緊盯著對方看，在Jimin走到自己面前時，他先是輕甩一下瀏海，表情一亮、小嘴微張開，露出小鹿般的眼神看向Jimin，身子微微向前、似乎想開口跟對方說話，但因Jimin沒看向他這邊、很快就走了過去，讓他錯失開口的機會。"},{"pid":"d989118b61c3fec3cb8411c5e963110b954dea2e","tid":515823,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T18:07:41.000Z","msg":"雖來不及跟Jimin打招呼，對方就從自己面前走過，但裴珍映眼神仍一路跟著Jimin，後來才默默跟著成員們一同座下，而他彷彿小粉絲見到偶像的反應，在網上引起不小討論，讓網友們看了紛紛表示「太可愛了」、「希望珍映可以跟Jimin變親」、「第一次看到珍映這麼開朗的表情」、「志訓喜歡V，珍映想跟Jimin打招呼」。"},{"pid":"8e7e8ff8908832d35c53fa65e87cc8521bd5872a","tid":515823,"uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/030452_9ef5e9d566a65bb56cab041cc83f7fc2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F030452_9ef5e9d566a65bb56cab041cc83f7fc2.gif&h=1cc7b5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢好似對佢有d意思咁既<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/014649_b95a8ce07426c8734fa0b13474888916.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F014649_b95a8ce07426c8734fa0b13474888916.png&h=d50085d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e663e88e406f5462d4d64bb07420b8209e90629","tid":515823,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T19:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DSZGxRJVQAATyI8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDSZGxRJVQAATyI8.jpg&h=b6b479bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先mbc歌謠<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/031624_81d83b805565ad1f32030c59ec514788.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F031624_81d83b805565